            "title": "Tracking dietary habits of cave arthropods associated with deposits of hematophagous bat guano: A study from a neotropical savanna",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Simone S.",
                    "lastName": "Salgado"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
