            "title": "Trophic structure of frugivorous bats in the Neotropics: emergent patterns in evolutionary history",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Mariano Sebastián",
                    "lastName": "Sánchez"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
